legendary bird of
fire. Every flap of its wings
creates a dazzling

flavor_text_entries.yellow:
A legendary bird
POKéMON. As it
flaps its flaming wings, even the
night sky will
turn red.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
This legendary
POKéMON scatters
embers with every flap of its wings.
It is a thrilling
sight to behold.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
This legendary
bird POKéMON is
said to bring early spring to
the wintry lands
it visits.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
Legendary bird
POKéMON. It is
said to migrate from the south
along with the
spring.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
MOLTRES is a legendary bird POKéMON
that has the ability to control fire.
If this POKéMON is injured, it is said to dip its body in the molten magma of a
volcano to burn and heal itself.
